Global Party Equipment Rental Service Market Insights
Party Equipment Rental Service Market size was valued at USD 7.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 12 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.25% from 2024 to 2030.

Party Equipment Rental Service Market Overview
The party equipment rental service market has witnessed significant growth in recent years due to an increasing demand for event planning and outdoor gatherings. The global market size for party equipment rentals is estimated to reach USD 40.7 billion by 2026, expanding at a CAGR of 4.5%. This growth is driven by a rise in disposable income, the increasing popularity of social events, and the expansion of the entertainment and tourism industry. Party rental companies are offering a wide range of services, including tents, tables, chairs, sound systems, lighting, and more, making them essential for events of all sizes and types. The market is expected to continue growing as consumer preference for convenience and cost-effectiveness drives demand across regions.

